data.description: Welcome to 531 Bates Avenue in Seville, OH. This 3-bedroom, 2-bath ranch home is a true masterpiece, featuring stainless steel appliances, a stylish kitchen island, and a spacious master suite with double vanity and a walk-in closet. The first-floor laundry adds convenience, while the full basement provides endless possibilities. Ryan Homes offers upgrades and this seller went the extra mile by upgrading to pristine white cabinets, a covered back porch for relaxation, and an egress basement window to unlock your basement's full potential. Plus, the basement is pre-plumbed for a full bathroom. You'll enjoy one floor maintenance free living when you close on this home. Bates Crossing's modest HOA includes landscaping and snow removal. While other buyers are waiting to build their dream home in Bates Crossing, yours is already built and ready to move right in. So much to enjoy with the future community pavilion and fire pit to meet up with friends and neighbors! This pet-friendly community goes above and beyond to accommodate pet owners, permitting fences to ensure a safe space for furry companions to roam. Their forward-thinking plans include the construction of a dedicated pet station. Enjoy easy commuting to Cleveland or Akron thanks to this home's prime location near routes 76/224 & 71. This home is just a 15 minute drive from the Historic Medina Square and 7 minutes to downtown Seville. Call your favorite Realtor today to schedule a private tour.
